description:

This yellow and white banner, is so cheery and perfect for spring and summer!  Add a touch of fun to your photos, or perfect for around the house, if you like the cottage, vintage, shabby style.  Even super cute in a little girls bedroom.  
Banner is approx. 75in.  Hung on twine, and with 5 scallop banners.  For each additional banner, it's $5 per banner. 
If there is a color combo you would like other than the yellow/white, please message me.  I'll be working on adding more colors to the shop soon.
